# Privacy Policy

**Arivu Kadhai – Kids Story AI**

Effective Date: 2026

Arivu Kadhai (“we”, “our”, or “us”) is designed to provide a safe and engaging storytelling experience for children. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle user information.

## 1. Information We Collect

Arivu Kadhai does **not collect, store, or share any personal information** from users.

All features, including story generation and saved stories, operate entirely on-device.

## 2. Children’s Privacy

This app is specifically designed for children under the age of 13. We strictly comply with child safety and privacy standards and do not collect any personal data from children.

## 3. Offline Functionality

Arivu Kadhai works fully offline. No internet connection is required to generate stories or access saved content.

## 4. Data Storage

Any saved stories or app data are stored locally on the user’s device using secure storage. This data is not transmitted outside the device.

## 5. Third-Party Services

This app does not use any third-party services, analytics tools, or advertising networks.

## 6. Data Security

Since no personal data is collected or transmitted, user privacy is fully protected.

## 7. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy in the future. Any changes will be reflected on this page.

